{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, the model can process the designer's responses and help generate functional analysis and ideas to resolve contradictions.",
    "Importantly, the proposed model does not function as a black box for problem-solving but rather aims to guide designers through the design process stages and foster insights.",
    "The model's performance was assessed using the GPT 3.5 API.",
    "The results indicate that the model's comprehensiveness surpasses its accuracy.",
    "Evaluation of the generated ideas reveals that machinegenerated ideas exhibit greater novelty, diversity, and quantity compared to those generated by TRIZ experts."
  ]
}